name: FV - test Claw Machine
description: Play the claw machine and win rewards! (yes really)

name: FV - Explorer Finds Item Museum
description: Click on explore items to go to their corresponding item museum page.

name: FV - BBCode Editor
description: Adds a BBCode formatting toolbar to Furvilla text editors.

name: FV - Search Item Button in Inventory
description: Adds a Search button inside the item inventory that takes you to the item museum.

name: FV - Clawtooth Bazaar Item Museum Links
description: Makes items in the Clawtooth Bazaar clickable so they link to their item museum pages.

name: FV - Single Click Fairy in Inventory
description: Single click using any fairy or openable item in inventory pages. To open items in their separate pae, go to your inventory and right click the fairy you want to open > open link in new tab. It will auto start, you click once to confirm the roll.

name: FV - Explorer TEST
description: Adds click progress to explorations. Does NOT handle events, the user needs to check for events regularly to keep the script working.

name: FV - Improved Min Level Displays
description: Displays the min level of equipment and inventory items, with color following the inherited text color.

name: FV - Feast Point Counter
description: Feast Point counter with batching, progress %, breakdown with quantities. Excludes spoiled food.

name: FV - Wishlist Public and Private
description: Wishlists in Furvilla. Search other users and update your own.

name: FV - Cloud's Gumdrop Snake Mini-game
description: Play a test round of snake with Cloud! Leaderboard available! Game works on /villager/56068

name: FV - Quick Links
description: Quick Links for all your Furvilla needs! Adds collapsible links, you may add/remove/rename and organize links that you may need on the go!

name: FV - Kitty Picross Mini-Game
description: Play picross (nonogram) with Wyll! Game works on /villager/456131

name: FV - Piper's Minesweeper Mini-game
description: Play minesweeper with Piper! Game works on /villager/456130

name: FV - Checkers Mini-game
description: Play checkers with Boe (random easy/medium/hard)! Game works on /villager/456129

name: FV - Gumdrop Snake Mini-game
description: Play a round of snake with Cloud! Game works on /villager/456128

name: FV - Snake Mini-game
description: Play a round of snake with Cloud! Leaderboard available!

name: FV - Sudoku Mini-game
description: Play a relaxing game of sudoku with Flow! Game works on /villager/455906

name: FV - Royal Higher or Lower Mini-game
description: Play against the Royal Fox with King Catrick. Guess if the next card drawn will be higher or lower than the previous one (1-21). Guess correctly as many times in a row as possible. Game works on /villager/455908

name: FV - Starr Slots Mini-game
description: Slot machine with Starr. Earn fake currency and climb the leaderboard!

name: FV - Minesweeper Mini-game
description: Play minesweeper with Piper!

name: FV - Sudoku Flow Mini-game
description: Play Sudoku with Flow!

name: FV - Magic 8-Ball Mini-game
description: Magic 8-Ball with predictions and a secret cat mode.

name: FV - Buckler Checkers Mini-game
description: Play a friendly game of checkers against Boe!

name: FV - Quick Craft Dock
description: Grid/list toggle recipes. Only click the recipe you want and watch it go. Auto starts and completes recipes. Works on the Alchemist, Blacksmith, Cook, and Crafter.

name: FV - Simon Says Mini-Game
description: Follow the colors with Simon!

name: FV CSS Editor (Villager Profiles)
description: test

name: FV - Necropost Warning (Forums)
description: Warn users if they are looking at old Furvilla threads.

name: FV - Stall Offers Panel
description: Adds a custom area in the stalls to offer for items, showing only latest offers per user, with sorting options. Clicking "Sell" opens a trading page to begin the transaction.

name: FV - Shuffle Mini-Game
description: Play shuffle (3 in a row) against other users. Go for the highest score while completing quests. Game works on /villager/456132

name: FV - Picross Mini-Game
description: Picross (Nonogram) puzzles for Furvilla. Randomly generated 10x10 boards.

name: FV - Tic Tac Toe Mini-Game
description: Escape the pirate crew by beating them at tic-tac-toe! Win each level to proceed. Lose and you restart.

name: FV - Rock Paper Scissors Mini-Game
description: Play rock paper scissors against the coolest grafitti crew out there. Best of 3!

name: FV - Sand Dollar Connect 4 Mini-Game
description: Play Connect 4 against a few Oceadome villagers! Who would've known they be so competitive.

name: FV - Royal Fox Higher or Lower Mini-game
description: Play against The Royal Fox. Guess if the next card drawn will have a higher or lower number than the previous one (range 1-21). Guess correctly as many times in a row as possible.

name: FV - Werewolf Mini-Game
description: Werewolf mini-game in a villager about box (test).

name: FV - Herbalist Multi-Plant Seed Limit
description: Expands seed dropdowns to match available (empty) Herbalist Pots.

name: FV - Inventory Search Bar
description: Adds the ability to search in your inventory. Includes Clear and Search buttons.

name: FV - Animal Husbandry Better Stable Management
description: Sort animals by item ID (rarity), toggle empty stables up/down, add Select All Stables/Animals toggles, and changes "Manage Stables" button to the header.

name: FV - Doctor Clinics Improved
description: Adds a one-click submit to the discharge confirmation. Picks the correct lowest % medicine by the default.

name: FV - Item Locator (Item Museum)
description: Adds a LOCATION under every item in the Item Museum.

name: FV - A User Furvilla Labs Page
description: Adds fa-cat icon that leads to the User Furvilla Labs page. The information regarding the available scripts is controlled by a villager!

name: FV - Better Trades Overall
description: Adds (autofilled) trade icon beside the Curio Case. Replaces transfer item icon with gift box. Adds auto "Check All" on top of the trades giving x1 of each. Adds "Max Owned" label and picks the biggest number in the drop down menu for that item.

name: FV - Warrior Potion Shortcut
description: Adds a "Potion Shortcut" next to the Battle Log for quick inventory access to Serpent brews and Golden Buff Dust.

name: FV - Highest Login Streak Tracker
description: Tracks and displays your highest login streak on Furvilla from the Daily Streak Page.

name: FV - Hide Sick Villager From Maintenance Market
description: Hide rows with sick villagers from the maintenance market list.

name: FV - Daily Panel Shortcut in Daily Streak
description: Adds quick-access buttons for daily collection features (The Daily Wheel and Warehouse Exchange)

name: FV - whiskerton battles
description: Whiskerton-fies the battleground enemies.
